<L>'For the light manners, the licentious deed?</L>
<L>'Forbid it Heaven!&mdash;O &s;mile my Child, and lure,</L>
<L>'To the maternal tran&s;ports, &s;oft, and pure,</L>
<L>'That lovely bo&s;om!&mdash;let thy opening bloom</L>
<L>'Charm my EMIRA, e'er &s;he yet con&s;ume,</L>
<L>'In guilty Plea&s;ure's fal&s;e and baneful flames,</L>
