<L>'Fall on the forehead of her beauteous Child.</L>
<L>'Pleas'd the maternal tribute to &s;urvey,</L>
<L>'EUGENIO ki&s;s'd the lucid drops away.</L>
<L>'Earne&s;t on him the Fair-One's moi&s;ten'd eyes</L>
<L>'Turn!&mdash;and &s;ome rays benign of &s;oft &s;urpri&s;e</L>
<L><PB N="69" REF="022137_0074_0FB6CD039A524030">'Meet his kind gaze&mdash;but ah! the tran&s;ient dawn</L>
<L>'Of virtuous feeling, in&s;tant is withdrawn;</L>
<L>'And tho&s;e mild beams, that Beauty be&s;t adorn,</L>
