<L><PB N="71" REF="022137_0076_0FB6CD1591FA3BE0">'To the pain'd hope, the &s;ecret dread pre&s;age,</L>
<L>'Th' ignoble triumph, and the &s;mother'd rage</L>
<L>'Of fatal Play;&mdash;the Ball's fatiguing ta&s;k,</L>
