<L>'The dup'd unhappy Fair-One's crimes &s;hall throw</L>
<L>'New fancied glories round the Boa&s;ter's brow.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>'Behold EMIRA, lo&s;t to faith, and &s;hame,</L>
<L>'Quench the la&s;t &s;park of her long faded fame</L>
