</LG>
<LG>
<PB N="76" REF="022137_0081_0FB6D16FADCCF9C0">
<L>Faintly the &s;ound of that known voice I hear,</L>
<L>"Oh my LOUISA!" &s;carce it meets my ear,</L>
<L>Le&s;t the imperfect &s;lumber &s;hould be found</L>
<L>Chas'd by the check'd involuntary &s;ound.</L>
